@altdef{@code[(chorus @i(snd) :delay @i(delay) :depth @i(depth) :rate @i(rate) :saturation @i(saturation) :phase @i(phase))] @c{[lisp]}}@\A chorus effect applied to @i(snd). All parameters may be arrays
