@altdef{@code[(midi-show-file @i(file-name))] @c{[lisp]}}@\Print the contents of a MIDI file to the console.

@codef{midi-show(@pragma(defn)@index(midi-show)@i(the-seq) [, @i(out-file)])} @c{[sal]}@*
